# Exploration: cat

## Rounds
  round 0: 73 isolated cumulative, 62 identical in round (single-phase)

## Observed: 10/10 flags
  10 solo, 0 via combination
  robustness: 10 robust, 0 moderate, 0 fragile

Aliases: -A = --show-all, -E = --show-ends, -T = --show-tabs, -b = --number-nonblank, -n = --number, -s = --squeeze-blank, -v = --show-nonprinting

## Solo (unique behavior)
  -A  # equivalent to -vET
    exemplar: "-A" "input.txt" "other.txt" in formatted_minimal
    | 28 only in this: first line$, second line with trailing spaces$, ^Iindented with tab$,     indented with spaces$, ^I ^Imixed tabs and spaces$
    | 28 only in ref: first line, second line with trailing spaces, 	indented with tab,     indented with spaces, 	 	mixed tabs and spaces
    base:
      first line
      second line with trailing spaces
      	indented with tab
          indented with spaces
      	 	mixed tabs and spaces
      
            ... (22 more)
    flag:
      first line$
      second line with trailing spaces$
      ^Iindented with tab$
          indented with spaces$
      ^I ^Imixed tabs and spaces$
      $
            ... (22 more)
